def extraction_date(txt_list):
    pattern_list=[r"\d{2}/[A-Za-z]{3}/\d{2} ?\d{1,2}:\d{2} ?(?:AM|PM)",r"\d+ days ago",r"\d+ week ago",r"\ Yesterday",r"\d+ hours ago"]

def calcul_duree (start_dates,end_dates,start_sprint,end_sprint):
    weekends = []
    Period =  []
    
    # Convert start_sprint and end_sprint to datetime.date objects
    #start_sprint_date = start_sprint.date()
    start_sprint_date = start_sprint
    print("calcul_duree: start_sprint_date: ", start_sprint_date)
    end_sprint_date = end_sprint
    print("calcul_duree: end_sprint_date: ", end_sprint_date)
    
    #calculer le nombre totale des jours 
    for start_date,end_date in zip(start_dates, end_dates):
        #Verifier les dates par rapport aux dates du sprint        
        if 'Noy' in start_date:
            start_date = start_date.replace('Noy', 'Nov')
        try:
            regex_patt = r'(\d{2}/[A-Za-z]{3}/\d{2})( ?)(\d{1,2}:\d{2})( ?)(?:AM|PM)'
            match = re.search(regex_patt, start_date)
            if match:
                # If there is no space between the year and the hour, add a space
                if not match.group(2):
                    start_date = re.sub(regex_patt, r'\1 \3', start_date)
                    match = re.search(regex_patt, start_date)
                if not match.group(4):
                    start_date = re.sub(regex_patt, r'\3 \5', start_date)
            StartDate = datetime.strptime(start_date,'%d/%b/%y %I:%M %p')    #StartDate is the first box of start_dates in the good format    
            start_task = StartDate
            print("start_task: ", start_task)
        except ValueError as e:
            print(f"Error: {e}")
    
        if (end_date == "00/jan/00 00:00 AM"):
            end_task = end_sprint_date
        else:
            regex_patt = r'(\d{2}/[A-Za-z]{3}/\d{2})( ?)(\d{1,2}:\d{2})( ?)(?:AM|PM)'
            match = re.search(regex_patt, end_date)
            if match:
                # If there is no space between the year and the hour, add a space
                if not match.group(2):
                    end_date = re.sub(regex_patt, r'\1 \3', end_date)
                if not match.group(4):
                    end_date = re.sub(regex_patt, r'\3 \5', end_date)

            try:
                end_task = datetime.strptime(end_date, '%d/%b/%y %I:%M %p')
            except ValueError as ende:
                print(f"Error: {ende}")        
        print("end_task: ", end_task)

        if start_task <= end_sprint_date and end_task >= start_sprint_date:
            debut_dans_periode = max(start_task, start_sprint_date)
            if debut_dans_periode == start_task:
                debut = StartDate
                current_date=StartDate
            else:
                print("DEBUT_Dans_Periode:",debut_dans_periode)
                objS = start_sprint_date.strftime('%d/%b/%y %I:%M %p')
                debut = datetime.strptime(objS, '%d/%b/%y %I:%M %p')
                current_date=debut

                debut = debut + timedelta(hours=9)
                print("La nouvelle date de debut est: ", debut)

            print("end_sprint_date: ", end_sprint_date)
            print("end_task: ", end_task)
            fin_dans_periode = min(end_sprint_date, end_task)
            print("fin_dans_periode: ", fin_dans_periode)
            if fin_dans_periode == end_sprint_date:
                objE = end_sprint_date.strftime('%d/%b/%y %I:%M %p')
                fin = datetime.strptime(objE, '%d/%b/%y %I:%M %p')         
                #fin = fin + timedelta(hours=17)
                print("La nouvelle date de fin est: ", fin)
            else:
                fin = end_task

            #calculer le nombre des weekend
            print(debut,fin)
            TotalPeriod = fin - debut
            print("La periode totale est:",TotalPeriod)
            Period.append(TotalPeriod)
            print("Period est:",Period)
            wd = 0
             
            #current_date = StartDate
            TotalPeriodSeconds = TotalPeriod.total_seconds() if TotalPeriod.total_seconds() else 0
            print(f"TotalPeriodSeconds:",TotalPeriodSeconds)
            TotalPeriodDays = TotalPeriodSeconds/ (24*3600)
            print(f"TotalPeriodDays before for:",TotalPeriodDays)
            if TotalPeriodDays.is_integer():  
                Days = TotalPeriod.days
                print(f"TotalPeriodDays.is_integer:Days =",Days)
            else :
                Days = TotalPeriod.days+1
                print(f"TotalPeriodDays.is_NOTinteger:Days =",Days)
            for i in range(Days):
                print(i)
                if current_date.isoweekday()>5: #current_date c'est quoi?
                    print("CURRENT DATE :",current_date)
                    wd+=1
                    print("wd:",wd)
                current_date+=timedelta(days=1)
            weekends.append(wd)
            print("WEEKENDS:",weekends)
            
    #Pour chaque jour on verifie s'il est un jour de semaine (1 a 5) ou un week end (6 et 7) en utilisant (isoweekday())
    #Calculer les durees de la tache
    Total_Period=[]
    print("Nombre de jours de weekend est: ",weekends)
    for TotalPeriod,wd in zip(Period, weekends):
        TotalPeriodSeconds = TotalPeriod.total_seconds()
        print(f"TotalPeriodSeconds:",TotalPeriodSeconds)
        TotalPeriodDays = TotalPeriodSeconds/ (24*3600)
        print(f"TotalPeriodDays in for:",TotalPeriodDays)
        TotalPeriodDays -= wd
        print(f"TotalPeriodDays: in for after weekend soustraction",TotalPeriodDays)
        Integerdays = int (TotalPeriodDays)
        Decimalpart = TotalPeriodDays - Integerdays
        DecimalpartInHours = Decimalpart *24
        if DecimalpartInHours >= 8:
            TotalPeriodDays = Integerdays + 1
        else :
            TotalPeriodDays = Integerdays + DecimalpartInHours/8
        Total_Period.append(TotalPeriodDays)   
        print(f"TotalPeriodDays: in for after weekend soustraction and good calculation of Decimalpart",TotalPeriodDays)
    #Calculer la duree total du travail de la tache   
    Duration = 0
    iter = 0
    for i,TotalPeriodDays in enumerate(Total_Period):
        iter += 1
        print(f"iter=", iter)
        Duration+= TotalPeriodDays
    print("La duree est :", Duration,'\n*************************************************')
    return Duration

def get_Date(prompt):
    while True:
        date_str = input(prompt)
        try:
            # Parse the input string into a datetime object with time set to 00:00
            date = datetime.strptime(date_str, "%d/%b/%y").replace(hour=0, minute=0)
            return date
        except ValueError:
            print("Format de date invalide. Veuillez saisir la date au format DD/Mmm/YY.")

def get_valid_date(): 
    while True: 
        start_sprint = get_Date("Entrer la date de debut (DD/Mmm/YY): ")
        start_sprint = start_sprint.replace(hour=9, minute=0)
        end_sprint = get_Date("Entrer la date de fin (DD/Mmm/YY): ")
        end_sprint = end_sprint.replace(hour=17, minute=0)
        if start_sprint <= end_sprint:
            return start_sprint, end_sprint 
        else:
            print("La date de debut doit etre anterieure ou egale a la date de fin. Veuillez reessayer.")

class DashPage:
    def __init__(self, driver):
        self.driver = driver

    def wait_and_click_button(self, button_id):
        button = wait.until(EC.visibility_of_element_located((By.ID, button_id)))
        button.click()

    def wait_and_capture_screenshot(self, element_id, screenshot_path):
        element = wait.until(EC.visibility_of_element_located((By.ID, element_id)))
        try:
            WebDriverWait(self.driver, 10).until(EC.visibility_of(element))
            element.screenshot(screenshot_path)
        except TimeoutException:
            print(f"echec de la capture de l'ecran pour {element_id}")

try:
    page = DashPage(driver)

    # Attendre que le bouton pour afficher les graphiques soit visible
    page.wait_and_click_button("show-graphs-button")
    
    # Capturer les captures d'?cran des graphiques
    graph_data = [
        ("status-pie-chart", "C:/Users/asiala/Desktop/stage/status-pie-chart.png"),
        ("histogram", "C:/Users/asiala/Desktop/stage/histogram.png"),
        ("grouped-bar-chart", "C:/Users/asiala/Desktop/stage/grouped-bar-chart.png")
    ]
    
    for element_id, screenshot_path in graph_data:
        page.wait_and_capture_screenshot(element_id, screenshot_path)
    
except TimeoutException:
    print("echec de l'attente ou du chargement des graphiques")

finally:
    # Fermer le navigateur WebDriver
    driver.quit()
